<subSubSection pageId="163" pageNumber="442" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="163.[1437,2643,1595,2575]" pageId="163" pageNumber="442">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1438,1788,2384,2417]" pageId="163" pageNumber="442">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Peruvian Rice Rat still faces taxonomic uncertainty, and there is no recent information on its natural history.
</paragraph>
